WEBVTT

00:04:29.316 --> 00:04:30.744
not belittled.

00:04:30.768 --> 00:04:33.377
They wanted to be
coached up, not torn down.

00:04:33.401 --> 00:04:35.983
They wanted to be motivated,

00:04:36.007 --> 00:04:38.313
not pressured or bullied.

00:04:39.476 --> 00:04:41.235
That was my time-out,

00:04:42.242 --> 00:04:43.937
and I chose to change.

00:04:45.689 --> 00:04:48.948
Being a dogmatic dictator

00:04:48.972 --> 00:04:52.525
may produce compliant,
good little soldiers,

00:04:52.549 --> 00:04:55.363
but it doesn't develop champions in life.

00:04:56.278 --> 00:05:00.443
It is so much easier, in any walk of life,